title: What Forced Riccitiello Out at Electronic Arts?
description:
March 18 (Bloomberg) -- Electronic Arts said John Riccitiello stepped down as chief executive officer and will leave the board. Cory Johnson reports on Bloomberg Television's "Bloomberg West." (Source: Bloomberg)
